data.caption: Atrucup
data.description:
15. ročník

2 dny ultimate (7 na 7- soft mixed- 2 žabky na lajně)
2 hřiště
8 - 12 týmů
1 koupaliště
1 hospoda
1 pivní závod

Spaní ve stanech.
Příjezd možný již v pátek večer.
Kromě celých týmů se nám mohou hlásit i jednotlivci do případného pick-up týmu.
Startovné obsahuje hřiště na hru, vody, dvě snídaně, jednu večeři, páteční občerstvení a sobotní kulturu. 
Startovné v podobné ceně jako v posledních letech, tj. 3000,-/tým a 200,- hráč. Přesněji bude upřesněno v dalším infomailu. Stejně tak jako téma párty.

data.caption: Trnava frisbee games
data.description:
Prihlaseno jako mix

Hello Ultimate players,

We would like to invite you and your teams to the very exciting and fun tournament wich will take place this summer in Slovakia - Trnava Frisbee Games. 

This event will not only host Ultimate clubs and U17 tournaments but also World championship in Freestyle frisbee, European Open championship in DogFrisbee and international DiscGolf tournament. That means around 700 frisbee players from all around the world at one place. Literally at one place - the tournament will take place in huge sports area with 7 full-sized football fields (4 reserved for Ultimate), backup gyms, camping, student rooms, hotel, dining and even newly reconstructed aquapark and wellness facility. Plus the beautiful centre of the historical (and student) town Trnava is just 5 minutes by walk. 

Trnava is well-connected to the airports in Bratislava and Vienna and also easily reachable by train or bus. You can also expect affordable costs of generally everything plus a nice players package.

Team registration for Ultimate is now open. http://www.trnavafrisbeegames.com/ultimate-registration/ 

We expect some interesting teams from all around Europe and exciting U17 tournament. You can expect smooth-going competition run by the team of experienced Czech and Slovak players (some of the WUCC 2010 organizers, members of Prague Devils etc.).

Browse the event website for more information and follow the facebook page for the fresh news. 


Soon we will start announcing registered teams. Will you be one of them? :)


Hope to see you in Summer in Trnava! 

Jakub Kostel
Event director

Feel free to contact me at info@trnavafrisbeegames.com with any questions.
